Available - heres a detail shot of a double bubbler I made not too long ago. Dub bubs have been one of my favorite shapes in the pipe game for a long time. I don't remember who it was exactly but I used to see an artist on glasspipes.org who made a number of them where the second chamber was like a hops inline (anyone have ideas as to who I'm talking about??) and this was before I even knew glass was in my future. I wanted one so badly, it was my dream piece but I didnt know how to get it. Instagram literally didnt even exist, my local headshops had nothing like it and I couldnt find anyone who had one on tokecity to even try and make an offer. As soon as I started blowing glass I decided that making one would be a goal of mine and this piece right here is a big step towards accomplishing that 🙏 "You must have long term goals to keep you from being frustrated by short term failures" - Charles C Noble
